Package: r4subscore
Title: Submission Confidence Index Engine for Clinical Submission Readiness
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R:
    person("Pawan Rama", "Mali", , "prm@outlook.in", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Converts standardized R4SUB evidence into indicator scores, pillar
    scores, and a Submission Confidence Index (SCI). Provides sensitivity
    analysis, explainability tables, and decision band classification to answer
    the question: are we ready for regulatory submission?
License: MIT + file LICENSE
URL: https://github.com/R4SUB/r4subscore
BugReports: https://github.com/R4SUB/r4subscore/issues
Depends:
    R (>= 4.2)
Imports:
    cli,
    dplyr,
    r4subcore,
    rlang,
    tibble
Suggests:
    testthat (>= 3.0.0)
Remotes:
    R4SUB/r4subcore
